## âš™ï¸ Installation & Setup

### 1 Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/Pavan-Kalyan112/Research-Paper-Fetcher-CLI.git
cd Research-Paper-Fetcher-CLI

### 2 Install dependencies using Poetry
```bash
poetry install
```

